{
  "workflow": {
    "id": 14841,
    "name": "Create LinkedIn posts from web pages using Airtable, Dumpling AI, Claude and PostPulse",
    "views": 0,
    "recentViews": 0,
    "totalViews": 0,
    "createdAt": "2026-04-06T21:50:11.602Z",
    "description": "### How it Works \nThis workflow takes web URL's from Airtable, extract URL data with Dumpling AI, creates attention grabbing LinkedIn post with Claude, and schedules post in PostPulse.\n\nSet up steps\n- **Airtable Trigger**: Triggers our workflow via the **URL Link** field in our base.\n- **HTTP Node**: 3rd party API call to Dumpling AI's extract endpoint to extract website data. web URL is sourced from Airtable base. \n- **Anthropic’s Claude**: Creates LinkedIn post using the extracted web summary from the HTTP node.\n- **Schedule a Light Post**: Schedule the posting date of our generated Claude post.\n- **Update Airtable Base**: Update G**enerated LinkeIn Post** field and **Scheduled** field in Airtable.",
